This Privacy Policy applies to the Discord Bot named ニキータ・パリク. We are committed to protecting the privacy of all users of our Discord Bot (“users”). This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect from you when you use our Discord Bot, how we use and store that information, and how we protect it.

Information We Collect:

We collect information from you when you use our Discord Bot. This includes:

• Your Discord's username, user ID and your Discriminator Tag
• Your Guild's name, icon and ID
• Your messages to the Discord Bot

We may also collect other information from you, such as language preference.

How We Use Your Information:

We use the information we collect from you to provide you with a better experience when using our Discord Bot. This includes:

• Responding to your messages
• Customizing the content we show you
• Improving the Discord Bot

We may also use your information for other purposes, such as for research and analytics.

Storage and Protection of Your Information:

We store your information on secure servers and use industry-standard encryption to protect it. We also take steps to limit who can access your information and ensure that it is only used for the purposes stated in this Privacy Policy.

Your Rights:

You have the right to request a copy of the information we have collected from you, to request that we delete your information, and to opt out of any marketing or other activities we may use your information for.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We recommend that you check this page periodically to ensure that you are aware of any changes.
